{"tid":1627410,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］記者朋友有啲嘢同大家講","createTime":"2019-10-05T15:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T08:44:45.000Z","uid":172909,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3d25c15460240b03147b7a4108781825b600992f","tid":1627410,"uid":172909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:46:59.000Z","msg":"大佬啊！係newsroom 睇直播個個都唔戴面巾，有啲竟然連口罩都唔帶！你知唔知真係好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先，戴口罩其實都唔太影響認到你個樣，你依家仲要唔戴！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你諗下啲狗搵返啲Live睇係幾咁易認到你。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其二，你哋唔係真係淆個閪法下話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理性分析下，你有戴罩比人捉到就要坐姐，如果當場捉唔到你就完全唔洗驚；但如果你無戴罩，啲狗就唔一定要當場捉到你都可以入非法集結！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />戴唔戴罩都會比人捉，但戴咗罩你走到就無事喎！唔係唔戴下話。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其三，唔戴罩唔單止會令自己更危險，都會令身邊嘅人更危險。你出得黎就要安全至上，好好保護自己個身份，同時大家blackblock 係互相保護緊大家。濫捕情況唔會因為你唔戴口罩而少左㗎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然唔戴好似好乖，但要記住依家係打緊仗㗎，加上蒙面法本身已經on9，當你行出黎就唔應該接受，應該要全部人都戴罩。<br />\n<br />\n長氣講多句，記得要戴面巾，最基本都口罩吖&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong>"},{"pid":"77dd82e71510a09d0a65a857a966556b473bbf22","tid":1627410,"uid":92885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:48:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"71ed69e343641aa2e1fdf008b725e27c24424d43","tid":1627410,"uid":172909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:49:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2dX7oxk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2dX7oxk.jpg&h=0c7c74b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無面巾就用tee，包到老母都唔認得你就啱！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n走個陣除底著返喺身又得，唔驚畀人周到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92db0441d9ffb22782e4092a6b950a831f00750a","tid":1627410,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:50:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c47be9411f310d4c6b653a06b3111eb43da6bc72","tid":1627410,"uid":172909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:51:23.000Z","msg":"推啊，屌你！"},{"pid":"6bf10bd635582a7f6793a3df0ea79cad3a3c6f5e","tid":1627410,"uid":172909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:54:23.000Z","msg":"睇返公司直播啲片，10個有8個佢真人係到我都認到啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05aa11fea5a324b60a190ef1b2361a4ac9042838","tid":1627410,"uid":172909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:56:10.000Z","msg":"我係仆街藍絲一定係啲片到cap鳩你哋相啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da8d3ddfb9ef5760c9b2df24fb7feb1b26d94104","tid":1627410,"uid":172909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:08:15.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"f42c9978e19335fcc4566ced477a6d5de5b2fe3c","tid":1627410,"uid":172909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:09:20.000Z","msg":"下次再見到你班友唔戴罩我cap曬你哋上連登啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"259baf75174abfe38148e4767d6f361db29d4597","tid":1627410,"uid":172909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:11:34.000Z","msg":"我要多啲人睇到啊！"},{"pid":"5e7637d33e1de9c0b59e78a4c6ee91974b7bae5d","tid":1627410,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20